I"\<p>Graduate students Courtney Krafczyk, Rebecca Holmes, Michelle Victora and JJ Wong, and undergraduate Sheldon Schlie were the winners of the <a href="http://www.osa.org/en-us/about_osa/newsroom/news_releases/2016/osa_honors_consumer_physics_scio_world_s_first_m/">OSA Enabled by Optics contest</a> with their video about the optics of fingerprint sensors! The video explains total internal reflection and other optics concepts with cartoons and demonstrations.</p>

